{
  "stem": "22840.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- we ate berries and drank from the-- from the very clear-- it was not rivers-- little springs that are so abundant in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Slovakia is a nice country, if they don't kill you all the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And we-- we stay in huts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There are huts in the mountains for hunters and for skiers and for shepherds.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was a totally agricultural community in that area.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So there were huts for the shepherds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- and we had milk and cheese from the shepherds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I don't recall how long we were on the road.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I recall it with great pleasure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sure my mother didn't think it was a great pleasure.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just the three of us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, But clearly somebody sympathetic and clearly somebody Christian.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know that we stopped a couple of times.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody opened the ambulance.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know if we stopped for roadblocks or we stopped for-- just stopped.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're not the only one on the road.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Eventually, we abandoned it and went from one place to another, and never to stay long.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The only place I remember staying long was Banska Bystrica.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not at all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew about the Tatra Mountains, which is not far away from there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Banska Bystrica was a name known to me, but not a city known to me because it was a big city.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] So we-- we arrived in that place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that-- that the first place that I remember that I stayed for a long time, the three of us, in an apartment in a-- in a place more organized than-- than just a hut.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was not in the mountain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember walking in Banska Bystrica.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
